    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Regarding adding the option for a future version, what about:\n- a `minPages` options (that mirrors the `maxPages`). If the number of pages is below that threshold, no widget is displayed\n- or allowing `autoHideContainer` to accept a function instead of a boolean that let users decide when hiding the widget.\n\nJust ideas on the top of my head, to be discussed.\n",
