    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@pixelastic Thanks for spending the time on this.\n\nI think the option name `minPages` would not represent the behaviour correctly and it would bring confusion when it's being compared with the semantics behind `maxPages`.\n\nHaving a function for `autoHideContainer` - basically a hook, is always useful. This is something very similar to what is considered for the search box widget with https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/776#issuecomment-172900988.\n",
