    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@hkdobrev Using the `render` event you should be able to hide/show the pagination: https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/documentation/#events\n\nI do not think we need any new API entry to deal with this case. Given your preference you might or might not want to hide the pagination.\n\nStill, being able to use a function as for the autoHideContainer seems like a nice idea, can you draft a new issue about it? Much like the #817 \n",
